Simplify Energy Use Data Collection

Input energy use data through a new simplified lightning web component to collect data faster and easier and increase data quality. Select the energy use type, enter the fields associated with the energy use entity, and upload any supporting documentation for the record.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions with the Net Zero Cloud Starter or Growth license.

Who: Simplified data collection is available to Salesforce users with the Net Zero Cloud Manager or Net Zero Cloud Admin user permission set, or Salesforce platform users with the Net Zero Cloud Light user permission set.
title: Simplify Energy Use Data Collection in Salesforce
